          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">F</hi>ROM <hi rend="italics">India</hi>'s burning Clime I'm brought,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-2" n="2">With cooling Gales like Zephyrs fraught.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-3" n="3">Not <hi rend="italics">Iris</hi> when she paints the Sky,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-4" n="4">Can shew more different Hues than I;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-5" n="5">Nor can she change her Form so fast,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-6" n="6">I'm now a Sail, and now a Mast.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-7" n="7">I here am red, and there am green,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-8" n="8">A Beggar there, and here a Queen.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-9" n="9">I sometimes live in House of Hair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-10" n="10">And oft in Hand of Lady fair.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-11" n="11">I please the Young, I grace the Old,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-12" n="12">And am at once both hot and cold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-13" n="13">Say what I am then, if you can,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-911-0871-line-14" n="14">And find the Rhime, and you're the Man.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
